=== Noun ===
'''usury''' (''[[countable]] and [[uncountable]]; plural'' '''usuries''')

#(''countable'') An [[exorbitant]] rate of [[interest]] in excess of any legal rates.
#(''uncountable'') The practice of [[lend]]ing money at such rates as are not legal or fair.

